This `ProgramService` class includes the following methods:

1. `createProgram(Program program)`: This method persists a new `Program` entity in the database.
2. `findProgramById(Long id)`: This method retrieves a `Program` entity from the database based on its ID.
3. `findAllPrograms()`: This method retrieves a list of all `Program` entities from the database.
4. `updateProgram(long id, Program updatedProgram)`: This method updates an existing `Program` entity in the database with the provided `updatedProgram` data.
